        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Centroctenus dourados sp. n., male IBSP 250608 (A–D), female IBSP 250607 (E–F). A left male palp, ventral view; B same, pro-ventral view; C retrolateral view; D prolateral view, E female habitus, dorsal view; F epigynum, ventral view. Abbreviations: C, conductor; E, embolus; LL, lateral lobes; MA, median apophysis; MS, median sector of epigynum. Scale bars: A−C = 1 mm; D, F = 0.5 mm; E = 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4424239/files/figure.png" .

